1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:55,540
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:59,159 --> 00:00:59,679
Your Majesty.

4
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,960
I've already investigated.

5
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,920
There's been
no movement in or out recently.

6
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:04,920
Could it be

7
00:01:05,959 --> 00:01:07,239
that it was all just my paranoia?

8
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,840
Mu Ruyi's body is right here.

9
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:13,239
But a woman
who looks just like her has turned up.

10
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:16,359
Is it a scheme or a coincidence?

11
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,040
It seems

12
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,640
I need to consider carefully

13
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:22,280
about how to care for my mother-in-law.

14
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:24,640
Perhaps

15
00:01:26,519 --> 00:01:27,840
she could be useful in other ways.

16
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:31,120
Your Highness, how have you been lately?

17
00:01:32,519 --> 00:01:33,319
I'm good.

18
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:35,599
You must not put yourself in danger
for my sake.

19
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:38,280
But rescuing my mother is urgent.

20
00:01:38,799 --> 00:01:40,200
I can't wait another moment.

21
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:41,959
Ling Xiao is indeed suspicious.

22
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,040
Fortunately, we had a body

23
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:45,319
buried at the mausoleum in advance.

24
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:47,519
I dare not imagine

25
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,519
the torment
Her Majesty must be enduring.

26
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,760
I must find a way

27
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,040
to use Ling Xiao's lingering guilt

28
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,200
and resentment toward me

29
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,640
and make my way back to the palace.

30
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,319
(The Butterfly Seal has to be removed)

31
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,840
(to deceive Ling Xiao.)

32
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,719
Ling Xiao,

33
00:02:29,159 --> 00:02:31,520
I will never forget this pain.

34
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,840
You will pay me back tenfold.

35
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:47,140
(Zhao Sisi, legitimate daughter
of the Prime Minister)

36
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,719
A court singer from a music house

37
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,439
dares to seduce His Majesty?

38
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:03,800
Let me see

39
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,759
just what kind of woman

40
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:08,240
has His Majesty so bewitched.

41
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:12,840
Who are you?

42
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:14,759
Don't you know me?

43
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:15,840
Listen up.

44
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:18,680
I am the Prime Minister's daughter,

45
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,439
the first noble lady of Dongqing.

46
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:23,199
I don't care.

47
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:24,560
It has nothing to do with me.

48
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:32,680
A temptress
who uses her zither to enchant men.

49
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,960
A lowly court singer,

50
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:37,039
dreaming of serving the King?

51
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:42,000
Look at your face.

52
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,560
It's truly pitiful and alluring.

53
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,639
I will destroy your face

54
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,319
and see if His Majesty will still

55
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,800
fall for you temptress.

56
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:51,199
No!

57
00:03:52,879 --> 00:03:55,080
Zhao Sisi, how dare you!

58
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:55,800
Get lost!

59
00:04:04,199 --> 00:04:04,840
Are you alright?

60
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:09,960
A music house has never been peaceful.

61
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,560
I'm used to

62
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:14,840
situations like this.

63
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:16,519
About what happened today,

64
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:19,240
I'll take it
as blood spilled to ward off ill fate.

65
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,639
Sir, please take this lady away now

66
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,720
and never come back

67
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,639
or make any more trouble.

68
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:30,120
The one I want to take

69
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:31,920
is you.

70
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,000
Your Majesty!

71
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,519
A lowborn woman from the pleasure houses

72
00:04:35,959 --> 00:04:38,120
is unworthy of
Your Majesty's noble status.

73
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:41,399
I was of lowly birth.

74
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,120
So what?

75
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:44,279
Guards!

76
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,199
- Yes!
- Yes!

77
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,399
Redeem Miss Liuli's freedom

78
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,000
and take her to the palace.

79
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:50,519
- Yes.
- Yes.

80
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:57,959
What are these?

81
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,600
Everything's in pairs.

82
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:02,319
You're a woman living alone.

83
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,120
You don't even have any luggage.

84
00:05:04,439 --> 00:05:06,000
I picked these out especially for you

85
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,319
to improve your life.

86
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,560
I can't cook.

87
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,160
I rarely even light a fire at home.

88
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:13,360
I wander everywhere.

89
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:14,879
These fine things are no use for me.

90
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,519
Didn't you say you were a countrywoman?

91
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:20,079
Who says every countrywoman can cook?

92
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,480
That's quite offensive.

93
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:24,920
I'm sorry, Miss Xia.

94
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,079
It's fine.

95
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:28,360
But I can cook for you in the future.

96
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:33,480
I'll do it.

97
00:05:35,199 --> 00:05:35,800
Why?

98
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:38,319
Watch your hands.

99
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,639
I was just trying
to serve you some rice.

100
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,199
I'm not used to

101
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:48,199
physical closeness with others.

102
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:49,439
Got it.

103
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,800
I'll be more careful next time.

104
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,360
If this continues,

105
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:58,199
you're going to break me.

106
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,519
Good thing I'm a military physician.

107
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,480
I can treat myself.

108
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:05,759
So?

109
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:07,240
How's my cooking?

110
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:12,040
I just don't want to waste it.

111
00:06:15,639 --> 00:06:16,759
What's so funny?

112
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,680
You have a good appetite.

113
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:19,879
You can eat, and you can fight.

114
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,240
I'm so thirsty...

115
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:45,959
I'm so cold...

116
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,319
Brother...

117
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:07,680
Brother...

118
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,839
What did you say?

119
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:11,560
I don't want to be bullied anymore.

120
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,720
I'm scared.

121
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:16,160
Brother...

122
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:18,120
- I'm so scared...
- Don't be afraid.

123
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,279
I'm here.

124
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,160
Your Majesty.

125
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:25,839
Your Majesty.

126
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:30,680
I'm here.

127
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,600
Everything will be alright.

128
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,639
Ever since my parents passed away,

129
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,680
I've wandered everywhere,

130
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,399
with no one to rely on.

131
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:48,959
I thought

132
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:51,519
that with my zither skills,

133
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:53,800
I could support myself.

134
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,199
But I never expected

135
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:57,720
that, whether in the music house

136
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,439
or outside it,

137
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:02,439
I'm bullied every single day,

138
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,560
and I can't get away from it.

139
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:07,199
Being of lowly birth,

140
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,199
my greatest wish

141
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:12,720
is to find a place of peace

142
00:08:14,759 --> 00:08:17,120
and live with dignity in this world.

143
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:20,279
But I was born
with red marks on my face,

144
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:23,319
and now my body is injured.

145
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,639
I can no longer play.

146
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,439
The dreamed-of peaceful life

147
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,399
seems even further away now.

148
00:08:38,639 --> 00:08:39,519
I promise you,

149
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,840
as long as I'm here,

150
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:45,519
no one will ever bully you again.

151
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,120
Your Majesty has redeemed my freedom,

152
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:51,320
giving me a new life.

153
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,799
I dare not ask for anything more.

154
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:18,159
Miss Liuli, are you here to laugh at me,

155
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:20,320
knowing I've been punished
by His Majesty?

156
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,840
I'm new to the palace and lost my way.

157
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:24,679
I'll take my leave now.

158
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:25,279
Stop right there.

159
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,200
Are lowborn court singers

160
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,639
ill-mannered?

161
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,519
You can't even bow properly.

162
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:36,480
I remembered.

163
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,360
You're a cripple now.

164
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:39,879
How about this?

165
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:41,799
I come from a noble family,

166
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:43,639
and my father serves as Prime Minister.

167
00:09:44,279 --> 00:09:45,879
If you humble yourself and kowtow to me,

168
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:47,879
you should
consider it your good fortune.

169
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:51,679
Kowtow!

170
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:55,440
I told you to kowtow!

171
00:09:58,399 --> 00:09:59,559
Kowtow now!

172
00:10:13,639 --> 00:10:15,279
Since you're a cripple,

173
00:10:15,919 --> 00:10:17,399
I'll let you off today.

174
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:20,159
If you ever show your face
before me again,

175
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:22,480
I'll take your worthless life.
